00:08:52.850 --> 00:08:56.390 align:middle line:10%
One of the important
components of well-being

00:08:56.390 --> 00:09:00.980 align:middle line:10%
is resilience, the capacity
to effectively cope

00:09:00.980 --> 00:09:02.330 align:middle line:10%
with adversity.

00:09:02.330 --> 00:09:04.640 align:middle line:90%
