other in our lives.

00:09:10.460 --> 00:09:13.530 align:middle line:84%
And how we respond
to that adversity

00:09:13.530 --> 00:09:16.170 align:middle line:84%
is a key attribute
of well-being.

00:09:16.170 --> 00:09:19.940 align:middle line:84%
>> So if I'm looking at
resilience as being the aspect

00:09:19.940 --> 00:09:22.340 align:middle line:84%
