naturally to flow in the river.

00:09:28.370 --> 00:09:30.870 align:middle line:84%
You naturally go
around the rock.

00:09:30.870 --> 00:09:35.420 align:middle line:84%
You naturally flow
into this tributary.

00:09:35.420 --> 00:09:38.260 align:middle line:84%
>> And it turns out that we can
actually learn to become more

00:09:38.260 --> 00:09:39.060 align:middle line:90%
resilient.

00:09:39.060 --> 00:09:44.780 align:middle line:10%
We can learn to recover more
quickly from a stressful event.

00:09:44.780 --> 00:09:48.440 align:middle line:10%
The evidence that we
have before us today

00:09:48.440 --> 00:09:52.070 align:middle line:10%
